      <title>波兰将于5月18日举行总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/poland-to-hold-presidential-election-on-may-18</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰将于 5 月 18 日举行总统选举，拉开执政联盟希望从民族主义反对派手中夺取的关键角色之争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/poland-to-hold-presidential-election-on-may-18</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗在委内瑞拉就职前加大镇压力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/maduro-ratchets-up-repression-ahead-of-inauguration-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派计划在全国范围内发起抗议活动，谴责尼古拉斯·马杜罗本周就任总统，委内瑞拉政府因此发动新一轮镇压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/maduro-ratchets-up-repression-ahead-of-inauguration-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国总理候选人淡化特朗普加入北约的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/german-chancellor-front-runner-downplays-trump-s-nato-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有望成为下一任德国总理的德国保守党人弗里德里希·梅尔茨淡化了美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普呼吁北约成员国将国防开支增加一倍以上的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/german-chancellor-front-runner-downplays-trump-s-nato-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:19:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普请求最高法院停止对他的封口费判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-jan-10-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普请求美国最高法院介入其封口费刑事案件，以阻止其 1 月 10 日的宣判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/trump-asks-supreme-court-to-halt-jan-10-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:18:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 发布 eBay 广告修复程序以遵守欧盟反垄断命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/meta-floats-ebay-ads-solution-to-comply-with-eu-antitrust-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 提出在 Facebook Marketplace 上发布分类广告竞争对手 eBay Inc. 的列表，以遵守具有里程碑意义的欧盟反垄断命令，该命令还附带 7.98 亿欧元（8.22 亿美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/meta-floats-ebay-ads-solution-to-comply-with-eu-antitrust-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:39:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国考虑在查戈斯协议中为毛里求斯支付前期费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-weighs-front-loading-payments-for-mauritius-in-chagos-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正考虑预先向毛里求斯提供资金，作为将查戈斯群岛（包括英美的一个重要军事基地）的主权割让给这个印度洋国家的一个加价协议的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-weighs-front-loading-payments-for-mauritius-in-chagos-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国保守党通过投票争夺马斯克的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-tories-vie-for-musk-s-attention-with-grooming-inquiry-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国反对党保守党周三在议会寻求投票，要求对所谓的儿童性侵团伙展开全国调查，试图给基尔·斯塔默领导的工党政府制造政治问题，同时赢得亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-tories-vie-for-musk-s-attention-with-grooming-inquiry-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言深化金融、能源等领域反腐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/china-vows-to-deepen-graft-fight-in-areas-like-finance-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府承诺将在金融、能源等广泛行业深化反腐倡廉建设，这表明国家主席习近平打击腐败官员的行动在可预见的未来还会继续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/china-vows-to-deepen-graft-fight-in-areas-like-finance-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国保守党对移民采取强硬路线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/german-conservatives-embrace-hard-line-on-migrants-to-combat-afd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有望成为下一任总理的德国保守党人正在加强其在移民问题上的立场，以抵御极右翼德国选择党（AfD）的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/german-conservatives-embrace-hard-line-on-migrants-to-combat-afd</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在税收斗争前召集关注 SALT 的共和党人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-calls-salt-focused-republicans-to-florida-before-tax-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有关延长 2017 年减税政策的斗争即将爆发之前，来自纽约、新泽西和加利福尼亚州的约 20 名共和党众议院议员应邀于周六在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的海湖庄园与他会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/trump-calls-salt-focused-republicans-to-florida-before-tax-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 21:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
